{"TopicId":128059,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Submarine ballast","CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T20:16:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T20:16:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m working\u00A0on a cool looking, relatively small submarine, the only problem is that it floats, despite being made of 99% full fuel tanks. I was just looking for tips on how to make working submarines, you know, ballast and all that, without having downward facing engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T20:21:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOre tanks of the same size are a lot heavier. Just don\u0027t forget to fill them before launch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T21:43:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat seemed to work, anyone else got any tips?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow","CreatedById":65767,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T00:08:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you have several ore tanks along the length of the submarine, if you don\u0027t fill them to the absolute max, you can move ore between them to trim the sub\u0027s attitude once you are underwater.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drew Kerman","CreatedById":103177,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T03:45:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwait and see what \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105198-roverdude/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022105198\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105198-roverdude/\u0022\u003E@RoverDude\u003C/a\u003E comes up with. He\u0027s already teased a mini sub so there must be something he added to get it to submerge properly. It could be a module you can apply to other parts as well\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RoverDude","CreatedById":105198,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T03:53:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do a few things. \u00A0Add a tweakable lead resource to weigh stuff down (so you can at least get in the ballpark), then add a ballast tank that takes in or expels water, which gives you fine control (and if you put a tank at each end, it makes balancing a breeze).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/u4PGGIV.png\u0022 alt=\u0022u4PGGIV.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T09:07:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222327342\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128059\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450410787\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105198\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RoverDude\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, RoverDude said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do a few things. \u00A0Add a tweakable lead resource to weigh stuff down (so you can at least get in the ballpark), then add a ballast tank that takes in or expels water, which gives you fine control (and if you put a tank at each end, it makes balancing a breeze).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/u4PGGIV.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022u4PGGIV.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/u4PGGIV.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWHAT. Where do I find this beauty?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow","CreatedById":65767,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T09:20:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCargo bays do something similar. \u00A0My sub uses 3 that start very partially open. \u00A0As soon as you close them it submerges.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoors open\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.88qv.com/KSP/ub3.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ub3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoors closed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.88qv.com/KSP/ub4.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ub4.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RoverDude","CreatedById":105198,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T10:32:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222327528\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128059\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450429642\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002211952\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaverickSawyer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, MaverickSawyer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWHAT. Where do I find this beauty?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn my twitch stream \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u00A0 Looking for a release Monday if all goes well\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drew Kerman","CreatedById":103177,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T11:54:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222327342\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128059\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450410787\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105198\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RoverDude\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, RoverDude said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do a few things. \u00A0Add a tweakable lead resource to weigh stuff down (so you can at least get in the ballpark), then add a ballast tank that takes in or expels water, which gives you fine control (and if you put a tank at each end, it makes balancing a breeze).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI figured it was something along these lines, similar to the setup you had for your balloons - which were great by the way I had a lot of fun with the blimp!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-18T20:04:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the help guys!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T07:53:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t wait to see the USI Sub Pack!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ThatOneBritishGuy...","CreatedById":144135,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T18:07:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps a spiritual successor for the Maritime Pack (which is sadly no longer operational) is in order?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}